.LP
A
positizzle or 0 value fo' \fItm_isdst\fP shall cause \fImktime\fP()
to presume initially dat Daylight Savings Time, respectively,
is or aint up in effect fo' tha specified time fo' realz. A wack value for
\fItm_isdst\fP shall cause \fImktime\fP() ta attempt to
determine whether Daylight Savings Time is up in effect fo' tha specified
time.
.LP
Local timezone shiznit shall be set as though \fImktime\fP() called
