.LP
Da relationshizzle between tha \fBtm\fP structure (defined up in tha \fI<time.h>\fP
header) n' tha time up in secondz since tha Epoch is dat tha result
shall be as specified up in tha expression given up in tha definition
of secondz since tha Epoch (see tha Base Definitions volume of IEEE\ Std\ 1003.1-2001,
Section 4.14, Secondz Since tha Epoch) erected fo' timezone and
any seasonal time
adjustments, where tha names up in tha structure n' up in tha expression
